Definition: a grand council or grand assembly used to resolve political conflicts or other national problems
Example: he convened a Loya Jirga that persuaded tribal leaders to acquiesce
Synonyms: Jirga, noun, location, Afghanistan, r, a, grand, council, or, assembly, used, to, resolve, political, conflicts, other, national, problems, he, convened, Loya, that, persuaded, tribal, leaders, acquiesce
Category: noun.group
